  "title": "Site Engineer #81798",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction of Buildings</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Site Engineer (Residential & Renovation)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Ubi</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday – Friday, 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support landed house, A&A and luxury home renovation works; ensure compliance with drawings/specs/method statements.</li><li>Coordinate daily site operations (subcons/suppliers/workers), materials, deliveries and logistics to meet schedule/quality.</li><li>Handle site measurements, verification, mark-ups/as-builts, inspections, and ensure safety/housekeeping standards.</li><li>Review Arch/Structural/M&E drawings, raise RFIs, resolve discrepancies, attend site meetings, and support TOP/CSC inspections/rectifications (if applicable).</li><li>Maintain site documentation (daily reports, progress updates, submissions, inspection and handover records) and other ad-hoc duties.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Civil Engineering, Building, Construction Management, or related discipline.</li><li>1–2 years of relevant site experience in residential/landed/A&A/renovation projects preferred.</li><li>Able to read drawings, coordinate across multiple trades, and manage basic site documentation (RFIs, inspections, progress tracking).</li><li>Knowledge of local safety practices and quality standards is an advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81798 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
